@startuml
!define AZURE_COLOR #0072C6
!define SIMPHERA_COLOR #FF6600

actor "DevOps Engineer" as DevOps
participant "Terraform" as Terraform
participant "Azure CLI" as AzureCLI
box "Azure Resources" #LightBlue
    participant "Azure Resource Manager" as ARM
    participant "AKS" as AKS
    participant "PostgreSQL Flexible Servers" as PostgreSQL
    participant "Storage Accounts (MinIO)" as MinIO
    participant "Key Vault" as KeyVault
    participant "Virtual Network" as VNet
    participant "Private Link" as PrivateLink
    participant "Log Analytics" as LogAnalytics
end box

DevOps -> Terraform: Initialize Terraform
Terraform -> AzureCLI: Authenticate
AzureCLI -> ARM: Deploy Resources

ARM -> VNet: Create Virtual Network
ARM -> AKS: Deploy Kubernetes Cluster
ARM -> PostgreSQL: Create PostgreSQL Servers
ARM -> MinIO: Create Storage Accounts
ARM -> KeyVault: Set up Key Vault
ARM -> PrivateLink: Configure Private Link
ARM -> LogAnalytics: Set up Log Analytics (Optional)

AKS -> VNet: Connect to VNet
PostgreSQL -> VNet: Connect to VNet
MinIO -> VNet: Connect to VNet
KeyVault -> VNet: Connect to VNet

PrivateLink -> PostgreSQL: Establish Private Connection
PrivateLink -> MinIO: Establish Private Connection

AKS -> LogAnalytics: Send Logs (Optional)
PostgreSQL -> LogAnalytics: Send Logs (Optional)
MinIO -> LogAnalytics: Send Logs (Optional)
KeyVault -> LogAnalytics: Send Logs (Optional)

ARM -> Terraform: Return Deployment Status
Terraform -> DevOps: Display Outputs

@enduml